UID:O6xpyMCjGHTVGIUc9ExJp
SUMMARY:NPA March Mania Plant Sale
DTSTAMP:20260322T022253Z
DTSTART:20260322T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:March is a great time to buy plants from a select group of loca
	l small nurseries and specialty growers who sell an amazing collection of 
	hard-to-find and old-time favorite perennials\, shrubs\, ferns\, grasses a
	nd more. Your support helps these growers thrive and prosper\, and in retu
	rn they can grow even more special plants for our gardens! \n\nThis is a ‘
	Farmer’s Market Style’ plant sale where you purchase plants directly from 
	each seller – bring your own small wagon/cart to carry your purchases back
	 to your car. The plant sale features plants from local growers. Visit the
	 NPA Border after shopping! Email for more info.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amci
	ty.com/events/#/details/npa-march-mania-plant-sale/17923223/2026-03-22T00\
	n\nFrom SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/npa-march-mania-plant-sal
	e/17923223/2026-03-22T00
LOCATION:Bellevue Botanical Garden\, 12001 Main St\, Bellevue\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-sports
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
